item.description:
Let's celebrate that The New England Hiking group is one year old! This is your group. Without its members its just a website. Thank you for a great first year!

We have almost 500 members, over 150 hikes, great winter hikes and warmer weather is coming.

All area Meetups and their members are welcome to join us for an evening of good friends, good food and conversation.


Directions and menu:CJ's Great West Grill Manchester
item.how_to_find_us: Watch for me. I'll have a Meetup table sign in the back of the bar area.
item.why: Let's break the ice and meet each other. Busy people can't always hike, but getting away for a few hours close to home is always fun. This is a hiker's meetup that the weather will not affect. It will only cost you the price of your meal.
item.name: Meetup at CJ's Great West Grill Manchester
